{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "山雪欲來", "storyInfo": "諾希斯炸毀大橋與鐵軌，正式宣戰。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g1_snowyforest", "screenadapt": "showall", "x": 0.0, "y": 20.0, "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來這種荒郊野嶺是想挖出什麼寶貝給我看？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然是打算殺人滅口。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就嘴硬吧。你在這裡被我殺人滅口，倒是個不錯的選擇。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就快到了。菈塔托絲，你對此地可還有印象？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這一帶，我沒記錯的話，通往謝拉格外的路早就因為橋樑被風雪毀壞而廢棄了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡本來就暴風雪頻發，連加固過的橋樑都難保安穩，人們也就放棄了對這邊道路的再開發。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在圖里卡姆的關口有多少人，菈塔托絲？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足以讓我知道恩希歐迪斯每天都在和誰交易什麼的程度。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你知道，近日有多少武裝人員和裝備從你的眼皮底下繞過，進入了謝拉格嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道要說，恩希歐迪斯繞開圖里卡姆，在這種地方也開闢了鐵路？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......怎麼可能。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，來了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可那條路前面是片峽谷......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不再是了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drawbridge", "volume": 5.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_essenceofevolution_intro", "key": "$m_bat_essenceofevolution_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不可能！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用裝置把橋樑、軌道、承重結構全都收在兩邊的懸崖山體中。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了掩人耳目，只在列車將要通過的時候再從山體中伸出架成橋樑......", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼簡單的構思，卻要用到多麼複雜的設計去實現。真讓我有些不捨。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 20.0, "xTo": 0.0, "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地面上新落的雪令人難以察覺地顫動著，一種細微的聲響在漸漸變強。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橋樑的軸承間亮起星星點點的火光，一如照亮謝拉格的文明燈火。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_train", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainwhistle", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trainlp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "StopSound", "attrib