": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "24_i14", "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明晃晃的金屬器物似煙花般飛濺而出，叮叮噹噹地撞擊在幾根頑強挺直的橋樑鋼筋上，然後向下徑直墜去。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毛皮製物在火焰中舞蹈，而精良的戰術服卻似乎對此無動於衷。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知是這一切來得太過突然，還是聲響麻痺了知覺，目睹這一幕的眾人只是呆呆地望著，久久說不出一句話。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有青年若無其事地揮舞著施術單元在雪地上呼喚起一陣陣漣漪。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他發動術法，讓一把明晃晃的制式軍刀輕輕滑行到腳邊，隨後一個抬手，武器已在手中。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的鍛造工藝。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh", "volume": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很鋒利。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種若隱若現的淺藍色紋理......不知各位有沒有在希瓦艾什家的礦區見過類似的金屬？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開門見山吧。你想從我這裡得到恩希歐迪斯的情報，而我想利用布朗陶家的勢力去對付他。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從一開始就說過，需要展示誠意的不止是我。因為我太清楚布朗陶家的做法了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果發現無利可圖，或者意識到自己根本無法對付恩希歐迪斯，你們甚至馬上就會把我抓起來向他邀功。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但時間已經變得緊迫。就算是我，也不能估算出恩希歐迪斯到底還打算送多少人，多少武器進來。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要立刻行動，在他將足夠的戰力瞞天過海送進謝拉格之前，摧毀他的運輸路線。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我還要阻斷你們的後路，如今你們已經是我的共犯。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便你們想選擇向恩希歐迪斯投降，各位也都和今天這場爆炸脫不了關係。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我截斷這條道路之後，恩希歐迪斯也未必能有足夠的兵力與阿克托斯正面開戰。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，你們已經別無選擇。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......來人，給我把諾希斯拿下！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "且慢！", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#3$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲，這算是你的回答嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，諾希斯，你搞錯了一個前提。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從一開始就不信任你，我不會輕易信任一個背叛者。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就在懷疑，你為什麼在被逐出喀蘭貿易後還能堂而皇之地四處亂晃。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原本以為恩希歐迪斯放任你的理由，或許是你所掌握的資訊無足輕重，你的背叛在他預料之中。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為他把你當作一個連你自己都不知情的煙霧彈來干擾我們，但現在情況不同了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他怎麼可能放任你自由活動，向別人洩露這種程度的機密？這麼重要的線路怎麼可能沒有把守的駐兵？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對，那可是恩希歐迪斯，他怎麼可能沒有防備。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少安毋躁，畢竟他們原本的任務是遮掩列車在雪上留下的痕跡。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "delay": 0.2, "volume": 1.0, "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_275", "name2": "avg_npc_275", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要太過分了，諾希斯。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容我向你介紹恩希歐迪斯暗中訓練的部隊，代號“山雪鬼”。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼，這......山雪鬼？！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們即將像古老傳說中的山雪鬼那樣，不歸化於耶拉岡德的威光，用最純粹的力量去挑戰信仰。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_275", "name2": "avg_npc_275", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說躲藏在高原雪山深處的山雪鬼。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們戴著詭異的面具，繫著巨大的鈴鐺，裹著獸類的毛皮。謝拉格的兒童聽到這個名字，都會一下哭出聲。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那畢竟都只是些傳說。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前這支部隊的穿著不難讓人聯想到從列車中散落的裝備。看到他們臉上所戴的面具，菈塔托絲忍不住打了個寒顫。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_275"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......老爺對你的寬容換來的竟是這等卑鄙的背叛。", "name": "“山雪鬼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_275"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把在場的人統統抓起來！", "name": "“山雪鬼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_275"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲，該你展現誠意了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，這筆帳，我之後再跟你算！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在開始，這裡將要發生一場雷擊造成的雪崩事故。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些被恩希歐迪斯秘密安排在此的手下不幸遭難失蹤。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g7_thoroughfare", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......部隊的名稱似乎是“山雪鬼”。在場的“山雪鬼”不多，似乎都被菈塔托絲他們活捉了。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外執掌載貨列車的兩名“山雪鬼”雖然生還，但也一樣遭到囚禁。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我親眼所見的部分就到這裡了，我自信自己沒有被任何當事人發現。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯肯定也不會將此視為單純的雪難吧。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士！我在這兒！", "name": "恩希亞"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為免希瓦艾什家生疑，我就先行告退，等候博士的下一步指示。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "崖心！;......;好久不見。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line244", "option2": "line249", "option3": "line253"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line257"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，看到博士沒事我就放心啦，之前他們都跟我說博士公務纏身，不便會面。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在大典真正結束之前，博士還得像這樣待在佩爾羅契家，我好著急。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line257"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士？你怎麼不說話，你應該沒事吧......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家沒欺負你吧！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line257"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實也沒那麼久啦......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過把博士請來後出了這麼多事，我也覺得時間好漫長。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我聽說，好像博士和阿克托斯先生他們相處得還不錯？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......想想也是理所當然，博士在羅德島的人緣就很好。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，有什麼我能幫幫博士的嗎？這一出又一出讓我很過意不去，我總想替博士做點能做的事情。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "幫我保護好恩希歐迪斯先生？;幫我向聖女大人問聲好？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line265", "option2": "line270"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line275"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？博士這話說的，有鐧在，老哥他哪裡需要我添亂。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過既然博士都這麼說了，我會留個心眼的。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line275"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐她最近應該也忙，連我也沒什麼機會去見她。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過如果確實有必要，到時候我就從山路攀上去偷偷見她好了。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，想幫上博士的忙，結果又讓博士替我操心了。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那跟我講講關於謝拉格的傳說，比如山雪鬼？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line281"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士是從哪聽說的呀？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個嘛，其實已經是相當古老的傳聞啦。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說千百年前，耶拉岡德在風雪中保護人們時，有一群山野精怪不接受祂的庇佑，其中——", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g10_manorhouse", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們已經確認到有多處軌道遭受類似破壞，損失已經清點完畢，修復工程需要一定時間。", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但更嚴重的是，在謝拉格與外界的進出路線中，原本完全由我方掌握的幾條已經被截斷。", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即是說，外部的力量現今無法輕易進入謝拉格。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我們各類資源和材料的儲備都還算充沛，在軌道修復前足以維持......", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不重要，我不是在說這些。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......此外，我們還確認到諾希斯和菈塔托絲有所接觸，並且曾在我們領地的邊界徘徊。", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士現在境況如何？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家的人已經不再對他嚴加監視。博士帶來的護衛十分謹慎，我們無法追蹤。", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，下去吧。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "希瓦艾什家戰士"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做得很絕。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須承認，稍有些出乎我的意料，但諾希斯理當能做到這個地步。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的信任真扭曲。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_257_1#9$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他為喀蘭貿易分憂這麼多年，他應當有能力在一些事上超越我的預想。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並非信任。這是要求，希瓦艾什家對人才的要求。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來以為，只有準備好肩負起整個謝拉格，才有資格從耶拉岡德肩上接過它。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三族議會和蔓珠院把這個擔子爛在那裡已經太久了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我，所以你和聖女才要肩負起謝拉格。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她最終或許會選擇這麼做。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_257_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我必須為下一步做準備。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}